/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The street is lined with lush green trees, providing a stark contrast to the clear blue sky above. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades hinting at the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in urban landscapes. Cars of different makes and models are scattered along the road, adding to the dynamic nature of the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the buildings and the expanse of the sky. The colors in the image are vibrant, with the green of the trees and grass standing out against the blue of the sky and the varied hues of the buildings.
